      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for your next adventure. While you might find a few minor signs of previous love, it runs smoothly and looks great both inside and out. It's a solid, high-quality ride that's ready to get back on the road today!",
